---
title: Sesame Shrimp with Scallion Rice and Roasted Zucchini
description: If you’re like us, you’ve seen a lot of stir-fries in your day. But thanks to our sweet caramelized glaze, aromatic rice, and sprinkle of crunchy sesame seeds, this one is bound to top them all. Plus, your kids will love it. Sounds like a win-win to us.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-shrimp-w39-ba47694c.jpg
